headline: Does GoDaddy’s AI Partnership and Smart Terminal Launch Reshape the Long-Term Bull Case for GDDY?
summary: In August 2025, Titan announced a partnership with GoDaddy to enhance GoDaddy's Professional Email offering for entrepreneurs and small businesses in developing markets, leveraging Titan's AI-enabled platform and planning a global rollout beginning in the third quarter of 2025. At the same time, GoDaddy introduced the Smart Terminal Pro, an advanced point-of-sale device featuring AI-powered inventory management and catalog creation, while updating financial guidance and reporting strong...
